Package: ggnet
Title: Network Visualization using the ggplot2 Package
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Hoover", email = "matthew.a.hoover@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: ggnet makes prettier network visualization using ggplot2 as the
    underlying plotting architecture rather than base graphics as many of the
    common social network pacakges do. It allows for an array of color themes and
    attributes, such as node size, color, shape, and directed/undirected edges.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 1.0.1),
    statnet,
    grid
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0.9000
